Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before transitioning to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases leading to 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average delay in starting 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' after 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Longest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' before any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' leading to a successful resolution ('Completed + Closed')
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases with more than one occurrence of this activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and the end of case where activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation occurs

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' across all cases in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Average duration difference between 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' observed in the event log
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - Implementation and the end of the case

Name: Distribution of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' duration across different countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Median duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the top 10 most frequent process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in cases that were resolved within the same day
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Comparison of average duration of 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' with 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' to identify bottlenecks
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Total elapsed time involving 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in the process variant leading to 'Completed + In Call' with the highest performance
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' and activity 'Completed + In Call'
